normalize-chiron:

normalize-chiron allows for easy interactive fitting of multip-band/order
spectra. normalize-chiron can output the normalized data as both a fits file and
a text files. It also makes plots of the orginal data with the fit and the final
normalized data for each order/band that is fit.

Basc Operation:
normalize-chiron is a modal program with modes of operation for
navigation/fitting of data, editting a previously produced fit, and for
editing/defineing a section of bad data to trim.


